{"tid":1332411,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」到底連登狗有冇版權","createTime":"2019-07-19T09:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T13:24:43.000Z","uid":212578,"like":1,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ddfa9f2d46ef5a4f9a9910ec1b11ba763cfb340a","tid":1332411,"uid":212578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:46:59.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我想用連登狗整game<br />\n表達下依家社會既議題<br />\n但係唔知有冇版權問題<br />\n可能會用佢既character 做其他animations<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ok冇問題拎去洗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔比錢買版權同牆國有乜分別"},{"pid":"7c6244d5ec6320f7d625fac7b0d6e9dc3a9ea4a7","tid":1332411,"uid":212578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:50:32.000Z","msg":"如果有要點樣買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb462585f0bb75e7e95af401c53f21df67e979cc","tid":1332411,"uid":29270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:50:39.000Z","msg":"版權是一項自動賦予的權利。在創作完成後，有關作品即擁有版權。版權與專利、商標及工業外觀設計等其他類別的知識產權不同之處，就是版權毋須在香港註冊，也可受香港法律保護"},{"pid":"2af825f162dda55c6b68d20bfd913d7cd14a0aad","tid":1332411,"uid":30179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:51:38.000Z","msg":"搵連仔授權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1514e70ceadc9f9b4a497d80100dd750b2dbabb","tid":1332411,"uid":212578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c6244d5ec6320f7d625fac7b0d6e9dc3a9ea4a7","tid":1332411,"uid":212578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:50:32.000Z","msg":"如果有要點樣買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7fc43fe2cfafef4e510b6a9b13a571d672d4cd8","tid":1332411,"uid":212578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T10:44:29.000Z